Greatest Cold Dry Mega Can

Greatest Cold Dry Mega Can from Premium Pouch Global is a premium product that offers 200 slimmed tobacco free portions with a clear taste of mint for a fresh nicotine pouch experience.

Greatest Cold Dry Mega Can delivers a nicotine level of 12mg/pouch. A refill can is always included!

column6: A mixpack with all flavors and strengths of VILD!
column7:
VILD Mixpack

Discover premium nicotine pouches and a variety of flavors and strengths in the VILD Mixpack! This mixpack contains the four different flavors of VILD that range from 5,6mg up to 11mg per pouch, perfect for those exploring different nicotine strengths.

The flavors consist of three different mint varieties in the Bris, Kuling and Strom, and a unique bitter-sweet flavor of licorice root, dried herbs and star anise in the Jaeger flavor.

VILD Mixpack includes
  • 1x VILD Bris (5,6mg/pouch)
  • 1x VILD Kuling (8mg/pouch)
  • 1x VILD Storm (11mg/pouch)
  • 1x VILD Jaeger (8mg/pouch)
